title: IAA Tonight | James Harden Out for a Month AND Brandin Cooks Stuck in Houston
description: Sixers All-Star G James Harden will be out for a month with a foot injury. How will this affect the Sixers and their championship aspirations? Plus, Houston Texans receiver Brandin Cooks will be stepping away from the team after not being traded before the deadline. Is this the right approach for the veteran receiver? Leger Douzable, Adam Pacman Jones, and Brandon Flowers gives their thoughts.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Adam Pacman Jones, Brandon Flowers)
